trans-unit.source: Represents an entry in either back or forward navigation history.
trans-unit.target: Hiermee geeft u een vermelding in de vorige of volgende navigatiegeschiedenis.

trans-unit.source: [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-wpf-md.md)] implements a navigation history service that stores one entry for each piece of content that has been previously navigated to, just like navigation history in [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ie](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ie-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-wpf-md.md)]een navigatie-geschiedenisservice met één vermelding voor elk item dat is is eerder genavigeerd, net als navigatiegeschiedenis in implementeert [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ie](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ie-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: Navigation history comprises two stacks, one that remembers back navigation history, and one that remembers forward navigation history.
trans-unit.target: Navigatiegeschiedenis bestaat uit twee stacks, één die back navigatiegeschiedenis onthoudt en één die forward navigatiegeschiedenis onthoudt.

trans-unit.source: An entry for the current item is added to back navigation history when a forward navigation occurs.
trans-unit.target: Een vermelding voor het huidige item is toegevoegd aan back-navigatiegeschiedenis als een forward navigatie plaatsvindt.

trans-unit.source: This occurs in the following situations: - The `Navigate` method is called (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>).
trans-unit.target: Dit gebeurt in de volgende situaties: - de `Navigate` methode is aangeroepen (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>).</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: - The `GoForward` method is called (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=fullName>).
trans-unit.target: -De `GoForward` methode is aangeroepen (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=fullName>).</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: - The forward button on the navigation [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] that is displayed from the current navigator ([!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)], <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>).
trans-unit.target: -De knop doorsturen op de navigatiebalk [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] die wordt weergegeven in de huidige navigator ([!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)], <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>).</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>

trans-unit.source: Likewise, an entry for the current item is added to forward navigation history before a back navigation occurs, which happens when: - The `GoBack` method is called (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>).
trans-unit.target: Ook kan een vermelding voor het huidige item wordt toegevoegd aan forward navigatiegeschiedenis voordat een back-navigatie plaatsvindt, dit gebeurt wanneer: - de `GoBack` methode is aangeroepen (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>).</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: - The back button on the navigation [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] that is displayed from the current navigator ([!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)], <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>).
trans-unit.target: -De knop terug op de navigatiebalk [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] die wordt weergegeven in de huidige navigator ([!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)], <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>).</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>

trans-unit.source: Each entry in back and forward navigation history is an instance of the JournalEntry class.
trans-unit.target: Elke vermelding back en voorwaarts navigatiegeschiedenis is een exemplaar van de klasse JournalEntry.

trans-unit.source: Each JournalEntry object encapsulates information about a particular navigation, including a name for the entry (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.Name%2A>), whether the entry is kept alive (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.KeepAlive%2A>) and the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] for the content that is navigated to (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.Source%2A>).
trans-unit.target: Elk object JournalEntry ingekapseld informatie over een bepaalde navigatie, inclusief een naam voor de vermelding (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.Name%2A>), of de vermelding is in stand gehouden (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.KeepAlive%2A>) en de [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] voor de inhoud die is genavigeerd (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.Source%2A>).</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.Source%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.KeepAlive%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.Name%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can retrieve all the JournalEntry objects in back navigation history by enumerating the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName> or <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName> properties.
trans-unit.target: U kunt alle JournalEntry-objecten in de vorige navigatiegeschiedenis ophalen met het inventariseren van de <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>of <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>Eigenschappen.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: For forward navigation history, you can retrieve all the JournalEntry objects by enumerating the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName> or <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName> properties.
trans-unit.target: Voor doorsturen navigatiegeschiedenis, kunt u alle JournalEntry objecten ophalen met het inventariseren van de <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>of <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>Eigenschappen.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: If you need to remove the most recent JournalEntry object from back navigation history, to prevent navigation to it, for example, you can call the `RemoveBackEntry` method (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName>), which removes the JournalEntry object and returns a reference to it.
trans-unit.target: Als u de meest recente JournalEntry-object verwijderen uit back navigatiegeschiedenis moet, om te voorkomen dat navigatie, bijvoorbeeld, u kunt aanroepen de `RemoveBackEntry` methode (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName>), waarmee het object JournalEntry verwijdert en retourneert een verwijzing naar deze</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: You cannot add JournalEntry objects to navigation history, however, because you can neither instantiate nor derive from JournalEntry, and because no type implements a member to do so.
trans-unit.target: U kan JournalEntry objecten toevoegen aan de navigatiegeschiedenis, echter, omdat u kunt geen exemplaar maken van of zijn afgeleid van JournalEntry en omdat het geen type implementeert lid om dit te doen.

trans-unit.source: However, you can add custom <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState> objects to back navigation history by calling the `AddBackEntry` method (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.AddBackEntry%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.AddBackEntry%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.AddBackEntry%2A>); <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService> adds the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState> object to an internally-created JournalEntry object, which is then added to the back navigation history.
trans-unit.target: U kunt echter aangepaste <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState>objecten navigatiegeschiedenis door het aanroepen van back-wilt toevoegen de `AddBackEntry` methode (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.AddBackEntry%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.AddBackEntry%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.AddBackEntry%2A>); <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService>voegt de <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState>object naar een object JournalEntry intern zijn gemaakt, dat wordt vervolgens toegevoegd aan de back-navigatiegeschiedenis.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.AddBackEntry%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.AddBackEntry%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.AddBackEntry%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState>
